Class DesignerViewController

  • java.lang.Object
    • contoller.DesignerViewController

  • public class DesignerViewController
extends java.lang.Object

      • setBlockTrialsNumber

        public void setBlockTrialsNumber(int numberOfTrials,
                        Block block)
        Add or delete the number of trials needed to match numberOfTrials. This function is threaded because it could result in waiting time on slow computers (mainly because of the way the things are rendered to the screen).
        Parameters:
        numberOfTrials - number of trials wanted in the block
        block - block to modify
